UniFi Network Controller is a centralized management system
for Ubiquiti UniFi products.

This is intended to be run as a nonprivileged user - by default, the
build script uses "unifi" as the user and /var/lib/unifi as the
default $HOME:

  # useradd -r -c "UniFi User" -d /var/lib/unifi unifi

If you wish to change the default run the script as follows:

  UNIFI_USER=nobody ./unifi.SlackBuild

